1
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,734
Blind auf dem Pedal

2
00:00:30,679 --> 00:00:37,793
Another hand's on the wheel to take me down to paradise

3
00:00:39,642 --> 00:00:41,237
Is this heaven or hell?

4
00:00:41,515 --> 00:00:48,234
Or am I trying to reach for something that don't exist

5
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,184
Here we are

6
00:01:13,758 --> 00:01:14,824
Going far

7
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:18,341
To save all that we love

8
00:01:20,236 --> 00:01:21,712
If we give

9
00:01:22,426 --> 00:01:23,407
All we've got

10
00:01:23,605 --> 00:01:26,765
We will make it through

11
00:01:29,617 --> 00:01:33,915
I know that I'm not who I want to be

12
00:01:34,241 --> 00:01:38,229
I'm running on high hopes again

13
00:01:38,464 --> 00:01:40,418
Make a change for the better now

14
00:01:40,646 --> 00:01:42,608
Feeling high on life somehow

15
00:01:42,822 --> 00:01:49,591
I know that one day I'll break free

16
00:01:54,872 --> 00:01:56,805
Reboot my heart

17
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,381
Rewrite my name

18
00:01:58,626 --> 00:02:03,528
<ruby>失敗<rt>ミス</rt></ruby>だらけのルートも抱いて

19
00:02:03,832 --> 00:02:04,965
Here we are

20
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,944
Never fall apart

21
00:02:07,236 --> 00:02:09,154
君となら

22
00:02:09,392 --> 00:02:11,354
何度でも start

23
00:02:11,593 --> 00:02:14,128
Out with all the self-doubt

24
00:02:14,324 --> 00:02:17,959
Do not kill that fear of thinking that I'll miss out

25
00:02:18,109 --> 00:02:20,165
Sorry that I must go

26
00:02:20,326 --> 00:02:26,852
I know that I'm not who I used to be

27
00:02:59,291 --> 00:03:03,155
傷だらけの地図を

28
00:03:03,403 --> 00:03:07,496
折りたたんでしまう前に

29
00:03:07,708 --> 00:03:10,768
君の声の在処

30
00:03:11,983 --> 00:03:16,069
座標に打ち込んだ

31
00:03:16,309 --> 00:03:18,876
ありえない未来さえ

32
00:03:19,331 --> 00:03:22,143
アップデートしていくなら

33
00:03:22,332 --> 00:03:24,716
曖昧な “さよなら”

34
00:03:24,927 --> 00:03:30,788
上書きしてしまえ

35
00:03:31,091 --> 00:03:34,039
Make a change for this hopeless road

36
00:03:34,201 --> 00:03:39,209
They don't want you to love me anymore now

37
00:03:39,443 --> 00:03:46,191
I know that I'm not who I want to be

38
00:03:46,156 --> 00:03:49,845
Now I'll break free

39
00:03:55,742 --> 00:03:57,415
Reboot my heart

40
00:03:57,706 --> 00:03:59,030
Rewrite my name

41
00:03:59,313 --> 00:04:05,333
崩れそうな今日さえ連れて

42
00:04:05,492 --> 00:04:06,208
Here we are

43
00:04:05,992 --> 00:04:07,063
Stronger than the scars

44
00:04:07,725 --> 00:04:10,159
君となら

45
00:04:11,344 --> 00:04:15,102
何度でも start

